(2, 71, 'Samsung Galaxy S7', 'post2', '<div class="row-container black-container" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1200px; background: #000000; color: #666666; font-family: telenor, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 40px; padding: 0px 30px !important;">\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 120px 0px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0px auto;">\r\n<div class="col-md-6-telenor" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left !important; width: 550.672px; margin: 0px 19.3125px 0px 0px !important;">\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 3.2rem; color: #ababab; margin-top: 0px;">Устойчиви на вода и  </h3>\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 3.2rem; color: #ababab; margin-top: 0px;">прах</h3>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 1.6rem; color: #ebebeb;">Galaxy S7 и S7 edge те следват навсякъде. Те са с теб под дъжда, край басейна, на плажа – без да се притесняваш, че ще ги намокриш. Все пак, тези телефони могат да издържат потопени във вода до 1.5 метра в продължение на до 30 минути. Освен това, те са добре изолирани от проникване на твърди тела и влага в корпуса им, утвърдено със сертификат IP68.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6-telenor" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; width: 550.672px; margin: 0px 0px !important 0px 19.3125px;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;" src="http://www.telenor.bg/sites/default/files/samsung-galaxy-s7-edge-water-resistant.jpg" alt="Прахоустойчив и водоустойчив смартфон Samsung Galaxy S7 | S7 edge" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row-container" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1200px; color: #666666; font-family: telenor, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">\r\n<div class="row no-padd" style="box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0px auto; padding: 120px 0px 0px !important 0px;">\r\n<div class="col-md-8-telenor right-fl" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right !important; width: 752px; margin: 0px 20.3281px 0px 0px !important;">', '\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 3.2rem; color: #333333; margin-top: 0px;">Революционна камера</h3>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 1.8rem; color: #333333;">Животът се случва навсякъде и по всяко време. За да уловиш</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 1.8rem; color: #333333;">правилния момент, Galaxy S7 и S7 edge имат камера с още</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 1.8rem; color: #333333;">по-бърз автофокус, а по-големите пиксели на сензора (1.4µm</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 1.8rem; color: #333333;">) и по-широкият отвор на блендата (F1.7 ) ви позволяват да</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 1.8rem; color: #333333;">правите ясни снимки дори при по-слаба светлина. С тях</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 1.8rem; color: #333333;">снимаш това, което виждаш – и то до най-малкия детайл.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 1.8rem; color: #333333;">Независимо дали заснемаш трик със скейтборд или духане</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 1.8rem; color: #333333;">на свещи по време на рожден ден, снимките ти ще са ясни,</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 1.8rem; color: #333333;">ярки и изпълнени с живот.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4-telenor camera-field" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; width: 364px; margin: 0px 0px !important 0px 20.3281px;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;" src="http://www.telenor.bg/sites/default/files/samsung-s7-camera-first.png" alt="Камера Самсунг S7" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row no-padd centered" style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center !important; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0px auto; padding: 120px 0px 0px !important 0px;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;" src="http://www.telenor.bg/sites/default/files/back-camera-s7.png" alt="Задна камера Samsung Galaxy S7" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row-container black-container" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1200px; background: #000000; color: #666666; font-family: telenor, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; padding: 0px 30px !important;">\r\n<div class="row no-padd" style="box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0px auto; padding: 120px 0px 0px !important 0px;">\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 3.2rem; color: #ababab; margin-top: 0px;">Спиращи дъха скорост и мощност</h3>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 1.6rem; color: #ebebeb;">Новият персонализиран CPU, мощният GPU и 4GB RAM създават впечатляваща комбинация. Galaxy S7 и S7 edge работят бързо и безпроблемно дори когато играеш игри, гледаш видео или теглиш приложения през тях.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row no-padd small-top-pad features-galaxy" style="box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 1200px; margin: 30px auto 0px; padding: 120px 0px 0px !important 0px;">\r\n<div class="col-md-4-telenor" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left !important; width: 345.797px; margin: 0px 19.3125px 0px 0px !important;">\r\n<div class="teaser-body" style="box-sizing: border-box; height: 106px;">\r\n<h3 class="chars" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; font-family: TelenorLight; font-size: 2.5rem; color: #ababab; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">CPU</h3>\r\n<h4 class="char-specs" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 10px; color: #999999; font-size: 1.6rem;">До 30% по-бърз от предшественика си</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<img style="box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;" src="http://www.telenor.bg/sites/default/files/galaxy-s7_hardware_cpu.png" alt="30% по-бърз CPU" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4-telenor" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 19.3125px; float: left; width: 345.797px;">\r\n<div class="teaser-body" style="box-sizing: border-box; height: 106px;">\r\n<h3 class="chars" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; font-family: TelenorLight; font-size: 2.5rem; color: #ababab; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">GPU</h3>\r\n<h4 class="char-specs" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 10px; color: #999999; font-size: 1.6rem;">До 64% по-бърз от предшественика си</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<img style="box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;" src="http://www.telenor.bg/sites/default/files/galaxy-s7_hardware-gpu-games.png" alt="Графичен процесор Samsung" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4-telenor" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; width: 345.797px; box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px !important; margin: 0px 0px !important 0px !important 19.3125px;">\r\n<div class="teaser-body" style="box-sizing: border-box; height: 106px;">\r\n<h3 class="chars" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; font-family: TelenorLight; font-size: 2.5rem; color: #ababab; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">4GB RAM</h3>\r\n<h4 class="char-specs" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 10px; color: #999999; font-size: 1.6rem;">Повишена от 3GB RAM</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<img style="box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;" src="http://www.telenor.bg/sites/default/files/galaxy-s7_hardware_4gbram.png" alt="RAM memory Samsung" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row-container" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1200px; color: #666666; font-family: telenor, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 120px 0px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0px auto;">\r\n<div class="col-md-6-telenor" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left !important; width: 579.656px; margin: 0px 20.3281px 0px 0px !important;">\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 3.2rem; color: #333333; margin-top: 0px;">По-голяма памет и по-дълъг живот на батерията</h3>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: TelenorLIght; font-size: 1.8rem; color: #333333;">С поддръжката на microSD имаш възможност да разшириш капацитета за съхранение, когато е необходимо. А с по-голямата батерия (S7: 3000mAh; S7 edge: 3600mAh) зареждането става още по-бързо.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6-telenor" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; width: 579.656px; margin: 0px 0px !important 0px 20.3281px;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;" src="http://www.telenor.bg/sites/default/files/samsung-s7_battery.png" alt="Battery Samsung Galaxy S7 | S7 edge" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 9, '2017-02-27 10:04:48', 335, '', '2017-03-04 09:12:23', 335, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-02-27 10:04:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","info_block_show_title":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"",